Title: Whirlpool — Built to stay
Author: wavelet-director

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - DAWN

First light crawls across a marble counter. A tilt-head stand mixer in graphite matte sits center frame, bowl polished to a mirror.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - DAY

The mixer's head tilts down. The whisk descends into pale dough. A slow spiral begins. Flour lifts in soft clouds.

CUT TO:

INSERT - THE BOWL

Macro: the dough folding over itself in slow, glossy ribbons. The whisk catches the light.

CUT TO:

INT. KITCHEN COUNTER - GOLDEN HOUR

The mixer is still. A pair of hands lifts a finished loaf from a board nearby. The mixer holds the frame like a monument.

FADE OUT.
